span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.scribd.com/doc/6635685/Bed-Making\">\"Bed Making\"</a>. <i>scribd.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">26 June</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=scribd.com&amp;rft.atitle=Bed+Making&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdoc%2F6635685%2FBed-Making&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABed-making\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> <i>A sample training document</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">McKay, Gary (1987). \"Chapter 2 - Doing Extras at Scheyville\". <i>In Good Company</i> (1998 ed.). Sydney, Australia: Allen &amp; Unwin. p.&#160;19. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-86448-904-9\" title=\"Special:BookSources/1-86448-904-9\">1-86448-904-9</a>. <q>He stepped into my mess of a room and by dinnertime he had run me through the whole gammut of how to set up the room in inspection order, and how to make the bed properly so the drillies could bounce a 20c coin off the counterpane</q></cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Chapter+2+-+Doing+Extras+at+Scheyville&amp;rft.btitle=In+Good+Company&amp;rft.place=Sydney%2C+Australia&amp;rft.pages=19&amp;rft.edition=1998&amp;rft.pub=Allen+%26+Unwin&amp;rft.date=1987&amp;rft.isbn=1-86448-904-9&amp;rft.aulast=McKay&amp;rft.aufirst=Gary&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABed-making\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Marable, Eileen (8 June 2012). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dvice.com/archives/2012/06/bed-makes-itsel.php\">\"Yes, yes a million times: Bed makes itself in 50 seconds\"</a>. <i>Dvice</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">26 June</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Dvice&amp;rft.atitle=Yes%2C+yes+a+million+times%3A+Bed+makes+itself+in+50+seconds&amp;rft.date=2012-06-08&amp;rft.aulast=Marable&amp;rft.aufirst=Eileen&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdvice.com%2Farchives%2F2012%2F06%2Fbed-makes-itsel.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABed-making\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://myluxurybed.co.uk/blogs/blog/a-chore-no-more-the-self-making-bed-is-here\">\"OHEA smart bed\"</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">26 June</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=OHEA+smart+bed&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fmyluxurybed.co.uk%2Fblogs%2Fblog%2Fa-chore-no-more-the-self-making-bed-is-here&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABed-making\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></